                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged to the having been before con<lb></lb>victed at this Court, in September</hi>, 1855, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**†—<rs id="t18680706-627-punishment-60" type="punishmentDescription">
